# Sentence Classification 

## Data collection
+ We use the data provided in the ACL 2017 paper “Scalable Bayesian Learning of Recurrent Neural Networks for Language Modeling” 
+ Link: https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/0B1HR6m3IZSO_VFIxR1VyaGREc0k

## How to use
Please run `run.sh` to reproduce our results in Table 2.
